## Careful mode

When `ROLEPOD_CAREFUL=1` is set (via `rolepod-codex.sh --careful` or env):

- Run all 5 simplicity questions explicitly before every commit
- Run all 5 test questions explicitly
- Spawn out-of-band reviewer for any change touching auth/billing/migrations
- Smaller increments: ≤3 files per commit, not ≤5
- Mandatory peer review even for small diffs
